    <div class="alert-box alert-green">
      <div class="alert-icon">&#9989;</div>
      <div><strong>Bottom line:</strong> MiniBox+ lung volumes are statistically equivalent to body plethysmography across healthy participants and those with obstructive and restrictive disease &mdash; and perform better than Helium Dilution, Nitrogen Washout, and CT in head-to-head comparisons.</div>
    </div>

