    <div class="tp-grid-comp">
      <div class="tp-comp-card" style="border-left:4px solid #1d4ed8;">
        <div class="tp-comp-lbl" style="color:#1d4ed8;">vs. NDD EasyOne Pro</div>
        <div class="tp-comp-text"><strong>"Their rep says it measures TLC — it doesn't perform the actual test."</strong> The EasyOne Pro uses a mathematical equation to estimate TLC. No plethysmography is performed, so you cannot bill CPT 94726. That's $55 per patient forfeited — $165,600 per year at 10 patients a day.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tp-comp-card" style="border-left:4px solid #0f766e;">
        <div class="tp-comp-lbl" style="color:#0f766e;">vs. Jaeger Vyntus Body</div>
        <div class="tp-comp-text"><strong>"Same capabilities — at double the price, requires a dedicated room, and $4,000 a year just to maintain."</strong> MiniBox+ sits on a desk, moves between rooms, any staff can run it, and has zero maintenance fees. Same CPT codes, same reimbursement, half the cost.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tp-comp-card" style="border-left:4px solid #7e22ce;">
        <div class="tp-comp-lbl" style="color:#7e22ce;">vs. MGC / Morgan (N&#8322; Washout models)</div>
        <div class="tp-comp-text"><strong>"N&#8322; washout systematically underestimates lung volumes in COPD and asthma patients."</strong> Gas can't reach air trapped behind narrowed airways. MiniBox+ plethysmography measures ALL gas in the thorax — truer disease picture, and you bill the higher CPT 94726 instead of 94727.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tp-comp-card" style="border-left:4px solid var(--amber);">
        <div class="tp-comp-lbl" style="color:var(--amber);">"We already have a body box."</div>
        <div class="tp-comp-text"><strong>"The MiniBox+ isn't a replacement — it's a complement."</strong> Run complete PFTs in satellite offices and exam rooms where a body box can't go. Any staff can operate it. Half the price. Zero maintenance. CHEST 2021 validated in 700+ patients at 11 medical centers.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

