                <td><div class="cell" style="text-align:center;"><div class="rh-tally" contenteditable="true" data-rid="r2" data-freq="1.5" oninput="rheumCalc()" onblur="rheumClean(this)" onfocus="rheumSel(this)">0</div></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><div class="cell">
                  <div class="rh-diag-name">Antisynthetase syndrome <span class="rh-risk rh-risk-h">high</span></div>
                  <div class="rh-diag-drug">&#8595; ILD often present at diagnosis &mdash; baseline then every 6 months</div>
                  <div style="font-size:10px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;font-style:italic;line-height:1.4;">No dedicated ICD-10 &mdash; combine the myositis code (M33.91) with an ILD code (J84.89).</div>
                </div></td>
